{"tid":522121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"惠康門口比個廢老屌","createTime":"2018-01-07T08:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T10:14:40.000Z","uid":90595,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"14ccf3fe8a2d2c287ce7705e48d0c6c1bf3f0f72","tid":522121,"uid":90595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T08:54:27.000Z","msg":"去惠康買完野出黎，見到有個廢老妹下妹下，一見我出黎就伸手問我拎野，<br />\n我心諗「唉，估唔到依家嘅香港，呀婆要執紙皮都算，依家收據咁細張紙都唔放過」<br />\n於是我好心，兩張收據都俾晒佢(貨品同visa兩張)<br />\n點知佢大大聲講左句「屌，痴撚線」<br />\n我唔識反應呆左呆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後尾先知原來佢係想收印花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c093561fe41f1f2471e95a4df50a8a3a47ded59c","tid":522121,"uid":68926,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T08:56:07.000Z","msg":"樓主第一次去惠康買野"},{"pid":"cac053c3350acbebe37194b707bd935537a657ea","tid":522121,"uid":90595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T09:24:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主第一次去惠康買野</blockquote><br />\n少囉 第一次見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0a3ecec5b430c90ecd665832a2822d2d9872cc","tid":522121,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T09:32:20.000Z","msg":"主動開口屌柒佢就o岩"},{"pid":"04376f1ca49ba0e7c11604f6ef517cfa76de7e99","tid":522121,"uid":151770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T10:14:40.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣珠城嗰間大撚把"}]}